  "text": "On the contrary, data of 218 SSc patients followed up in a Hungarian University-Based Centre [CITATION_1] evidenced 10 patients with malignancies; one of them was a 53-yearold woman with cervical cancer. Authors indicated that the SIR versus general population was 37.0, but the interval of confidence was not calculated, so that the finding cannot be reliable.",
